data.description: Don't miss your chance to explore this stunning two-story residence located in the highly sought-after Mallard's Lake Community. The Dupont Plan, a true gem, welcomes you with an open and spacious design that seamlessly combines the Living, Dining, and Kitchen areas. Step into the Kitchen, where you'll find exquisite cabinets, sleek granite countertops, and a suite of Stainless-Steel Appliances, including a Range with Microwave hood and Dishwasher. It is here you can access and walk out to the deck to view the backyard, trees, and lake with a walking path around the lake and access to fishing. Convenience reigns with one bedroom and a full bathroom conveniently located on the first floor. All other bedrooms, including the primary suite, are nestled on the second floor. The primary suite boasts a private bath with dual vanity sinks and a generous walk-in closet, providing a serene retreat. Two additional well-sized bedrooms on the second floor share another full-sized bath. Adding to the appeal, this desirable plan offers an extra Loft Space, perfect for versatile use, and a Walk-in upper-level Laundry room, ensuring practicality and ease in your daily routine. Large partially finished daylight basement with outside access that leads to the lake. It has two windows and stubbed for a fourth bath and has electric and studded walls. This home offers comfort, style, and a sense of belonging in the Mallard's Lake Community. Make this dream home yours today! Ask about the Seller Assumable Loan!
